page.title: 10HOMELIFE IN ENFILD
page.content: Sunday is the only day that my family are together. We wake up at 7.30am and have a cooked breakfast. Then we get the paper. At 9.20am we go to St. Michael and All Angels' Church. At 10.30am we go to Edmonton Swimming Pool. After we have been swimming we go home and get our dog, Annie, and take her to either Hilly fields or Whitewebbs Parks. When we get home we have lunch. Usually we have either roast lamb or roast pork. Once every two months we have roast beef. After lunch we watch television or use our computer. At 3.00pm we either go to my Nan's or she comes to us. At 5.00pm I feed my rabbit, Topsy, then I have something to eat. At 9.00pm I usually go to bed.
